has an extraordinary presence.

156
00:08:29,180 --> 00:08:30,340
I really want to see him.

157
00:08:30,340 --> 00:08:31,180
But

158
00:08:31,180 --> 00:08:32,860
you don't allow me to glance around,

159
00:08:32,860 --> 00:08:34,340
so I can't see anything.

160
00:08:34,580 --> 00:08:35,980
In this world, all men

161
00:08:36,220 --> 00:08:38,780
share similar facial features.

162
00:08:38,780 --> 00:08:40,420
What's truly rare to encounter

163
