189
00:10:03,380 --> 00:10:04,740
the security system of the Guanque Hall

190
00:10:04,740 --> 00:10:06,060
is the most rigorous.

191
00:10:06,380 --> 00:10:07,060
At present,

192
00:10:07,060 --> 00:10:08,380
