to see them?

196
00:10:17,540 --> 00:10:18,660
It's just different.

197
00:10:21,060 --> 00:10:23,380
Master and Madam spent money

198
00:10:23,460 --> 00:10:24,940
to arrange this visit for us today,

199
00:10:24,980 --> 00:10:26,940
just so that before entering
the palace for schooling,

200
00:10:26,940 --> 00:10:29,460
the Crown Prince
could have a good impression of you.

201
00:10:29,860 --> 00:10:31,540
Don't let those young ladies
steal the lead.

202
00:10:33,100 --> 00:10:34,180
One should view
the exhibition in silence,

203
00:10:34,580 --> 00:10:35,700
