hidden silk threads.

221
00:11:50,900 --> 00:11:53,860
From top to bottom, they're everywhere.

222
00:11:56,820 --> 00:11:58,540
The other end of the threads

223
00:11:59,340 --> 00:12:01,940
is connected

224
00:12:01,940 --> 00:12:03,340
to forty-nine hidden bells.

225
00:12:05,020 --> 00:12:07,140
