the folk culture of Shengdong.

256
00:13:55,700 --> 00:13:56,620
It symbolizes

257
00:13:56,620 --> 00:13:59,260
the power that devours any misfortune
daring to invade our home.

258
00:14:00,580 --> 00:14:01,260
Your Highness,

259
00:14:01,460 --> 00:14:03,500
